	* Tomboy/Watchers.cs: Fixed Gtk-WARNING message 'Unknown tag
	  gtkspell-misspelled' by correctly connecting/disconnecting the
	  TagApplied-event in the NoteSpellChecker addin. Fixes bug #507249.

