	Introduce drag and drop so users can drag a note into a notebook
	in the Search All Notes Window:

	* Tomboy.mdp: Added NotebooksTreeView.cs.

	* Tomboy/RecentChanges.cs: Use NotebooksTreeView so drag and drop
	  will work.

