	  libtomboy/Makefile.am, Tomboy/NoteTag.cs: Patch from
	  Gabriel de Perthuis to allow note text colors to
	  be readable with different contrast themes.  His patch
	  includes code from David Trowbridge's libcontrast.
	  Fixes #489559.

