	* Tomboy/Plugins/GalagoPresence.cs: Initial commit, very broken.

	* libtomboy/gtksourceprintjob.c: Fix missed conversion from
	GTK_IS_SOURCE_VIEW -> GTK_IS_TEXT_VIEW.

