2004-09-18  Alex Graveley  <alex@beatniksoftware.com>

	* TrayIcon/libtrayicon/Makefile.am: Install libtrayicon.so into
	pkglibdir.

	* TrayIcon/Makefile.am: Install TrayIcon.dll into pkglibdir.

